query:
SELECT 
  atem.id as templateId,
  atem.templateName,
  ats.id as sectionId,
  ats.sectionTitle,
  COUNT(atq.id) as questionCount
FROM auditTemplates atem
LEFT JOIN auditTemplateSections ats ON atem.id = ats.auditTemplateId
LEFT JOIN auditTemplateQuestions atq ON ats.id = atq.auditTemplateSectionId
WHERE atem.templateName LIKE '%Daily%'
GROUP BY atem.id, atem.templateName, ats.id, ats.sectionTitle
ORDER BY atem.id, ats.displayOrder;
